---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Resume" description="Karry Shi 的个人简历与作品项目">
  <section class="resume-stage max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="resume-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:items-end border-b border-border pb-12">
      <div class="motion-in">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Resume</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-light text-white leading-tight mb-6">Karry Shi</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          视觉设计、AI 视频与网页工具实践者。关注怎样把真实问题整理成可发布的作品：
          从素材梳理、内容结构、视觉表达，到静态网站和轻量互动工具上线。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="motion-in motion-delay-1">
        <div class="resume-avatar" data-tilt aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="avatar-grid"></div>
          <div class="avatar-ring"></div>
          <div class="avatar-core">
            <span>K</span>
          </div>
          <div class="avatar-chip chip-web">WEB</div>
          <div class="avatar-chip chip-ai">AI</div>
        </div>

        <div class="tilt-card mt-5 rounded-sm border border-border bg-surface/60 p-6" data-tilt>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted font-mono mb-4">Contact</p>
          <a href="mailto:shikairui11@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline font-mono text-sm">
            shikairui11@gmail.com
          </a>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="https://karry.asia" class="text-xs text-zinc-300 border border-border px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">karry.asia</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/karry1155" class="text-xs text-zinc-300 border border-border px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="motion-in grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] py-12 border-b border-border">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-white mb-3">核心能力</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          更擅长从具体场景出发，把零散内容整理成清晰的视觉和产品体验。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          ['真实问题拆解', '从学习、内容和传播场景里发现具体痛点，并拆成可执行的小步骤。'],
          ['AI 协作流程', '用 AI 辅助完成内容整理、题库清洗、视频生成、视觉方案和迭代复盘。'],
          ['网页作品落地', '能独立完成静态网站、互动页面、作品集内容和 Cloudflare Pages 发布。'],
          ['反馈驱动迭代', '根据真实使用反馈调整入口、信息层级和功能优先级，必要时敢于回滚重做。'],
        ].map(([title, body]) => (
          <div class="tilt-card border border-border bg-surface/50 rounded-sm p-5" data-tilt>
            <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-2">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">{body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="motion-in grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] py-12">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-white mb-3">实践方向</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          当前作品主要围绕网页、AI 视频和视觉系统展开。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          我会继续把作品集当成一个持续更新的个人工作台：每个项目都从一篇整理好的笔记开始，
          再通过 GitHub 和 Cloudflare Pages 发布成可访问的网页。
        </p>
        <p>
          近期重点是把 AI 生成内容转化成更完整的交互体验，例如滚动叙事网页、新闻视觉化页面，
          以及能解决真实学习问题的小工具。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .resume-stage {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .resume-glow {
    position: fixed;
    left: var(--cursor-x, 70%);
    top: var(--cursor-y, 24%);
    z-index: -1;
    width: min(34rem, 80vw);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.14), rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.03) 38%, transparent 68%);
    filter: blur(18px);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: left 180ms ease-out, top 180ms ease-out;
  }

  .motion-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(22px);
    transition: opacity 700ms ease, transform 700ms ease;
  }

  .motion-in.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .motion-delay-1 {
    transition-delay: 120ms;
  }

  .tilt-card,
  .resume-avatar {
    transform:
      perspective(900px)
      rotateX(var(--tilt-x, 0deg))
      rotateY(var(--tilt-y, 0deg))
      translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    transition: transform 180ms ease-out, border-color 180ms ease-out, background-color 180ms ease-out;
    will-change: transform;
  }

  .tilt-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.36);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045);
  }

  .resume-avatar {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 260px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 2px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 38%, rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.18), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015));
  }

  .avatar-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 28px 28px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 45%, black, transparent 72%);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .avatar-ring,
  .avatar-core {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }

  .avatar-ring {
    width: 150px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.55);
    box-shadow: 0 0 44px rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.1);
    animation: slow-spin 12s linear infinite;
  }

  .avatar-ring::before,
  .avatar-ring::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 18px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: inherit;
  }

  .avatar-ring::after {
    inset: -16px;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-top-color: rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.5);
  }

  .avatar-core {
    display: grid;
    width: 96px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    place-items: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.42);
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #e8ff47;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 28px rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.12);
  }

  .avatar-chip {
    position: absolute;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232, 255, 71, 0.28);
    background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.72);
    color: #e8ff47;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    padding: 0.28rem 0.48rem;
  }

  .chip-web {
    left: 1.25rem;
    bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .chip-ai {
    right: 1.25rem;
    top: 1.25rem;
  }

  @keyframes slow-spin {
    to {
      rotate: 360deg;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .motion-in,
    .tilt-card,
    .resume-avatar,
    .resume-glow {
      transition: none;
    }

    .avatar-ring {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const motionItems = document.querySelectorAll('.motion-in');
  const tiltItems = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[data-tilt]');
  const root = document.documentElement;
  const reduceMotion = window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches;

  const revealObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((entry) => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
        revealObserver.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.18 });

  motionItems.forEach((item) => revealObserver.observe(item));

  if (!reduceMotion) {
    window.addEventListener('pointermove', (event) => {
      root.style.setProperty('--cursor-x', `${event.clientX}px`);
      root.style.setProperty('--cursor-y', `${event.clientY}px`);
    }, { passive: true });

    tiltItems.forEach((item) => {
      item.addEventListener('pointermove', (event) => {
        const rect = item.getBoundingClientRect();
        const x = (event.clientX - rect.left) / rect.width - 0.5;
        const y = (event.clientY - rect.top) / rect.height - 0.5;
        item.style.setProperty('--tilt-x', `${y * -7}deg`);
        item.style.setProperty('--tilt-y', `${x * 7}deg`);
      });

      item.addEventListener('pointerleave', () => {
        item.style.setProperty('--tilt-x', '0deg');
        item.style.setProperty('--tilt-y', '0deg');
      });
    });
  }
</script>
